<h2>Weather as Language</h2>

<p>I wanted to make something that operated as both a functional tool and a visual experience. To be useful, the system needed structure. Creating a consistent visual language would ensure... By using each data point like a word in a sentence, I could convey complex weather conditions through just a few components.</p>

<p class="emph">Thinking of weather as a language permitted clarity through consistency</p>
