<section>
  <h5>Troubleshooting</h5>

  <p>On its own, the temperature wave moved as intended. But when I combined it with the typography, the frame rate would plummet as soon as the program launched.</p>

  <p>The issue occurred because image masks were redrawn each frame. Old masks weren't purged from the system's memory. Rather than treating the mask like a container, I reversed it, making it a flat layer that sits on top of the wave.</p>
</section>
